
<center>
!form reply
$table_header
 $table_tr
  <td align=center>One series will have</td>
  <td>
   !set nw_qnum=$user_qnum
   !formselect nw_qnum from 1 to 9
   exercices.
  </td>
 </tr>
 $table_tr
  <td align=center>Level of severity</td>
  <td>
   !set nw_qcmlevel=$user_qcmlevel
   !formselect nw_qcmlevel from 1 to 9
  </td>
 </tr>
 $table_tr
  <td align=center>Time limit </td>
  <td>
   <input size=7 name=nw_scoredelay value="$user_scoredelay"> seconds.
  </td>
 </tr>
 $table_tr
  <td align=center>Number of items shown in multiple choices : </td>
  <td>
   !set nw_qcmpresent=$user_qcmpresent
   !formselect nw_qcmpresent list 2,3,4,5,6,7,8 
  </td>
 </tr>
 $table_tr
  <td align=center>Give solution (if available) ? </td>
  <td>
   !default nw_presentsol=$user_presentsol
   !formselect nw_presentsol list 0,1,2 prompt never,if the score is not maximal,always
  </td>
 </tr>
 $table_tr
  <td rowspan=4>&nbsp;</td><td>
   !set nw_check=$user_check
   !formcheckbox nw_check list 1 prompt Always contain good reply.
  </td>
 </tr>
 $table_tr
  <td align=left>
   !formcheckbox nw_check list 2 prompt Penalty for bad replies in multiple choices.
  </td>
 </tr>
 $table_tr
  <td align=left>
   !formcheckbox  nw_check list 3 prompt Show good reply.
  </td>
 </tr>
 $table_tr
  <td align=left>
   !formcheckbox nw_check list 4 prompt Allow hint (if available).
   !let tmp=!replace word expert by $ in $special_parm2
  </td>
 </tr>
 $table_tr
 <td colspan=2 align=center>
  <input type=submit value="$wims_name_tosave">
  <input type=hidden value="1" name="step">
 </td></tr>
</table>
</form>
</center>
<p><small>You can put two numbers into the time limit,a smaller limit followed by a bigger one.
In this case, the first limit starts score reduction, which will got to 0 if the second limit is reached.
</small>
